@Changed structure tag of Photo CD library base to PhotoCDLibrary
Eliminated (bogus, IMHO) warnings caused by assigning ~0 to
    UWORD values
@
text
@/*** photocdbase.c **********************************************************
 *                                                                          *
 *  $Id: photocdbase.c,v 40.3 93/11/19 17:42:15 jjszucs Exp Locker: jjszucs $
 *  photocd.library                                                         *
